      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean 5k sounds okay but i read online that some people do way more than that to fix a deficiency really quickly. if i take the 50k for just 10 days or 2 weeks, isn't that basically just a shock to the system to get the levels up? i don't really see why that would be a big deal since it's not a long term thing.",
